=========================================================
HIGH VOLTABE OUTPUT TABLE
=========================================================

    IN FROM SIG-GEN     HV OUTPUT
    ---------------     ---------
        4.0                 24 KV
        4.5                 27
        5.0                 31
        5.5                 34
        6.0                 37   ==>    pri=60  sec=3.9 kv  vm-out=37.0 kv  watt-meter=105
        6.5                 39

space between coils approc 1/2 to 5/8 inch

